dent Senate has talked about doing some community service with the feeder patterns for Northwest, including Kensler, Peterson, McCollom and Wilbur.<\/p>\n<p>\u201cMaybe they will be more excited knowing the tradition,\u201d advisor Sarah Gegen said.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>September Events for COTY:<\/p>\n<p>9\/11 patriotic dress for United Way Week<\/p>\n<p>9\/12 Anything Goes assembly<\/p>\n<p>9\/16 volleyball<\/p>\n<p>9\/18 choir concert<\/p>\n<p>9\/24 Powderpuff<\/p>\n<p>9\/26 assembly<\/p>\n<p>9\/30 soccer<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>With a new advisor and meetings almost every day during 9th hour, Student Senate is making changes to increase Northwest school spirit and student participation. \u201cIt will be 100 times better. We are already planning and making decisions that will involve everybody at Northwest. [We\u2019re] really making Student Senate the best it can be,\u201d Student&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":3068,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"ngg_post_thumbnail":0,"footnotes":""},"categories":[459,4,12],"tags":[299,301,300],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3064"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3064"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3064\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3067,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3064\/revisions\/3067"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.northwestexplorer.org